---
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Data Retention Schedule — GroupsMix"
  description="How long GroupsMix retains user data, logs, webhook payloads, and abandoned accounts."
  canonical="https://groupsmix.com/data-retention"
  cssFiles={["/assets/css/legal.css"]}
>

        <div class="legal-container">
            <section class="legal-hero">
                <span class="legal-hero__icon">&#128197;</span>
                <h1>Data Retention Schedule</h1>
                <p class="legal-hero__subtitle">How long we keep each category of data, and when it is deleted.</p>
            </section>

            <nav class="legal-nav">
                <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
                <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
                <a href="/data-retention" class="active">Data Retention</a>
                <a href="/about">About</a>
                <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
                <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
                <a href="/support">Support Center</a>
            </nav>

            <span class="legal-meta">&#128197; Last updated: April 2026</span>

            <div class="accordion" id="accordion">

                <div class="accordion__item open">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="true">
                        1. Overview
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel s-507687">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>This schedule supplements our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
                            It describes how long GroupsMix keeps each category of data and when it is erased or anonymized.
                            Every access, export, and deletion request is recorded in our internal DSAR audit log
                            so we can evidence compliance on demand.</p>
                            <p>You can exercise your data-subject rights at any time from the
                            <a href="/settings">Privacy section of your settings</a>:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Download my data</strong> — returns a JSON bundle of everything we hold for your account.</li>
                                <li><strong>Delete my account</strong> — scrubs personal data immediately and queues your account for permanent erasure after a 30-day grace period.</li>
                                <li><strong>Privacy preferences</strong> — opt out of marketing, analytics, or personalization at any time.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        2. Retention Schedule
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <table class="s-473e6b">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th class="s-df9954">Category</th>
                                        <th class="s-df9954">Retention</th>
                                        <th class="s-df9954">Trigger for deletion</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Account profile &amp; contributed content</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Until account deletion + 30 days</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">User-initiated delete or abandonment policy (below)</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Abandoned accounts (no sign-in &gt; 24 months)</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">24 months, then soft-deleted</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Inactivity sweep → 30-day grace → hard delete</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Authentication / server logs</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">30 days</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Rolling TTL on log storage</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Webhook payloads &amp; delivery receipts</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">90 days</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Required to support replay &amp; fraud review</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Rate-limit counters (KV)</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">≤ 1 hour</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Auto-expiry via KV TTL</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Contact-form submissions</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">12 months</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Scheduled purge job</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Financial records (payments, payouts)</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">7 years</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Legal obligation — retained in anonymized form after account deletion</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">DSAR audit log</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">5 years</td>
                                        <td class="s-a916f4">Regulatory evidence of data-subject request handling</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        3. Account Deletion Flow
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>When you request deletion from the settings page we:</p>
                            <ol>
                                <li>Re-authenticate you with your password and a CAPTCHA challenge.</li>
                                <li>Immediately scrub personally identifiable information from your profile (email, display name, bio, phone number).</li>
                                <li>Flag the account for hard deletion in 30 days.</li>
                                <li>Invalidate active sessions so the account can no longer be accessed.</li>
                            </ol>
                            <p>During the 30-day grace period you can contact support to cancel the deletion. After the grace period our scheduled purge job removes the account permanently along with all content that cascades from it
                            (comments, messages, tips, marketplace listings, job applications, reading history, and feed interactions).</p>
                            <p>Financial records required by law (invoices, tax receipts, payout history) are retained in anonymized form for 7 years.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        4. Abandoned Accounts
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>Accounts that have not signed in for 24 consecutive months are flagged for soft deletion by the inactivity sweep.
                            We email the last known address and wait a further 30 days before running the same hard-delete pipeline as user-initiated deletions.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion__item">
                    <button class="accordion__trigger" aria-expanded="false">
                        5. Changes to This Schedule
                        <svg class="accordion__chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion__panel">
                        <div class="accordion__content">
                            <p>If we shorten any retention window we apply the change retroactively. If we extend a window we notify active users at least 30 days in advance via the email address on file and publish an updated version here.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

<Fragment slot="scripts">
<script is:inline>
    document.querySelectorAll('.accordion__trigger').forEach(function (btn) {
        btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
            var item = btn.closest('.accordion__item');
            if (!item) return;
            var panel = item.querySelector('.accordion__panel');
            var isOpen = item.classList.toggle('open');
            btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', isOpen ? 'true' : 'false');
            if (panel) panel.style.maxHeight = isOpen ? panel.scrollHeight + 'px' : '';
        });
    });
</script>
</Fragment>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* inline-styles: migrated */
.s-473e6b { width:100%;border-collapse:collapse; }
.s-507687 { max-height:600px; }
.s-a916f4 { padding:var(--space-2) var(--space-3);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-secondary); }
.s-df9954 { text-align:left;padding:var(--space-2) var(--space-3);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-primary); }
</style>
